root: ^This is a box of things you wern't able to take when you left your parents house
^Do you want look inside of the box?

Yes: ^On closer inspection, it reveals to be the few toys you were given as a child. A bear  once full of color now lifeless of color and infested with dust.
^Touching  makes you remember when you first got this toy and was filled with excitement, back then your parents were much more stable in terms of their reationship.
^...I wish things stayed the same as back then...
